public class MsLunch {
        private long c1 = 0;
        private long c2 = 0;
        private Object lock1 = new Object();
        private Object lock2 = new Object();
        public void inc1() {
            synchronized(lock1) {
                c1++;
            }
        }
        public void inc2() {
            synchronized(lock2) {
                c2++;
            }
        }
    }
